<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome aboard, <%= @user.first_name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully created an account with grouPACT. The email registered to your account is (obviously) <%= @user.email %>.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      The site is currently in Alpha, so please bear with us if you run into any bugs. More importantly, please share those experiences with us so that we can work quickly to correct them. You can reach us at grouppact@gmail.com - we'll do our best to respond within the day.
    </p>
    <p>
      Now, on to the fun stuff. To login to the site and get started, just follow this link: <%= @url %>. Happy planning!
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
